thread.title: Parkland students walk out to say "ENOUGH" to gun violence

title: Parkland students walk out to say "ENOUGH" to gun violence
text:
Parkland students walk out to say "ENOUGH" to gun violence 1:13pm EDT - 00:31 
Students at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School in Parkland, Florida walked out of school on Friday, joining thousands of other students across the country who are demanding tighter gun laws. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
